STATE
v.
Ronell Eugene JACKSON. No. 258P06. Supreme Court of North Carolina. June 29, 2006. William P. Hart, Senior Deputy Attorney General, Robert F. Johnson, District Attorney, for State of NC.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 10th day of May 2006 by Defendant for Appeal:
